733400.name: Tyd wag vir Niemand - Soundtrack
733400.description:
This is the Soundtrack for Tyd wag vir Niemand and includes all of the mesmerizing music contained in the game.

Get ready to go on an audio journey that will take you to another dimension, where time stands still and nothing
is what it seems.

With 12 diverse and unique songs you can take the sounds of Tyd wag vir Niemand with you wherever you go.

Track-list:

1. Tyd begin
2. Horlosie
3. Kristalle
4. Parkie
5. Grot Druppels
6. Gang van Meubels
7. Digitale Alarm
8. Spiraal Trappe
9. Sand en See
10. Die Groot Maan
11. Sprokies
12. Tyd is Goed
733400.supported_languages:
英语*
*具有完全音频支持的语言
